      "id": "age-verification-online-purchase",
      "sector": "retail",
      "title": "Age verification for online purchases",
      "summary": "An online shop confirms a customer is old enough to buy an age-restricted product before it can be added to the cart, without learning their date of birth or identity. The shop acts as the relying party and requests a simple over-18 proof from the customer's wallet over OpenID4VP. Because only the age attribute is disclosed, the flow is privacy-friendly by design and removes the friction of uploading ID documents during checkout.",
      "organizationName": "Neovo",
      "productionDeployment": "no",
